41779dae-dcc7-4dca-be6a-c981095354ff.title: Mourner
41779dae-dcc7-4dca-be6a-c981095354ff.text: Do you have a problem traveller?

15a623d1-cfef-46fb-af07-30fd2060be2b.title: <player>
15a623d1-cfef-46fb-af07-30fd2060be2b.text:
No, I just wondered why you're wearing that outfit...
Is it fancy dress?

ddf34227-7c0c-4826-a2c9-897c16e2e401.title: Mourner
ddf34227-7c0c-4826-a2c9-897c16e2e401.text: What are you up to with old man Edmond?

4f6cc6ca-2cdf-4cb6-8d2a-277140ac9601.title: <player>
4f6cc6ca-2cdf-4cb6-8d2a-277140ac9601.text: Oh, you know about that then?

8c5b2092-252f-4ed4-a7f1-da8cb9b0eca4.title: Mourner
8c5b2092-252f-4ed4-a7f1-da8cb9b0eca4.text:
We know about everything that goes on in Ardougne.
We have to if we are to contain the plague.

c741f74d-50bd-4d77-8544-826756876225.title: <player>
c741f74d-50bd-4d77-8544-826756876225.text: Have you see his daughter recently?

0e15b6cd-033f-41ba-bdf7-3253c7284e56.title: Mourner
0e15b6cd-033f-41ba-bdf7-3253c7284e56.text:
I imagine she's caught the plague. Either way she won't
be allowed out of West Ardougne, the risk is too great.

1800a7b3-105e-44aa-b5d7-c03563119c10.title: Note
1800a7b3-105e-44aa-b5d7-c03563119c10.text: this mourner roams just outside Edmonds home

2f9bcf08-7663-43ce-a2a5-ace9266e37fe.title: Mourner
2f9bcf08-7663-43ce-a2a5-ace9266e37fe.text: Your hands are covered in mud.

303e00bf-157a-4d10-b061-9ba38e749204.title: Mourner
303e00bf-157a-4d10-b061-9ba38e749204.text: Funny, you don't look like the gardening type.

d1e31c1d-d6da-405e-b5f1-cac36abebcb0.title: <player>
d1e31c1d-d6da-405e-b5f1-cac36abebcb0.text: Oh no, I love gardening! It's my favorite pastime.

17e68b7d-44c9-459f-be15-9d08165aca41.title: Mourner
17e68b7d-44c9-459f-be15-9d08165aca41.text:
If I find you attempting to cross the wall I'll make sure
you never return.
